OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,FCampaigners in St Paul's in Bristol
OL,7,Fsay they are fed up with overflowing
OL,8,Fbins, rubbish by their homes and waste
OL,9,F"stewed on the street".
OL,11,FResidents are calling for an improved
OL,12,Fwaste service and a more effective
OL,13,Freporting system to tackle flytipping.
OL,15,FOn the morning of Saturday, 28
OL,16,FFebruary, Bristol Waste held drop-in
OL,17,Fsessions for residents to try and
OL,18,Ftackle ongoing issues. They say it's a
OL,19,Fcomplex picture, but "understand
OL,20,Fpeople are rightly frustrated."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]{D@VOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
