OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,FEmma Reynolds has lived in the area
OL,7,Ffor nearly two decades and says the
OL,8,Fproblem started with the introduction
OL,9,Fof communal bins and mini recycling
OL,10,Fcentres around 16 years ago.
OL,12,FThey have become flytipping hotspots,
OL,13,Fbut Emma also believes Bristol Waste
OL,14,Fmust do more to stop rubbish piling up.
OL,16,FShe said: "There's always been a
OL,17,Fproblem since they (the communal bins)
OL,18,Fcame in. They're hugely expensive to
OL,19,Frun, and they attract flytipping and
OL,20,Fmess around the bins.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,F"For all these years, we've been stuck
OL,7,Fin a situation where there isn't any
OL,8,Fway of reporting issues because there
OL,9,Fis nothing set up for mini recycling
OL,10,Fcentres.
OL,12,F"Anything we report as an issue, we're
OL,13,Ftold it's flytipping. You have to ring
OL,14,Fup, wait for an hour and speak to
OL,15,Fsomeone.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,F"But sometimes it's simply that the
OL,7,Fbin hasn't been emptied, there's a
OL,8,Fhuge mountain of waste, birds are
OL,9,Fripping it open, and it's stewed on
OL,10,Fthe street. It's been going on for
OL,11,Fyears."
OL,13,FEmma, along with her friend Tara
OL,14,FMiran, are part of a campaign group
OL,15,Fcalling for a series of improvements,
OL,16,Fwhich includes more regular cleaning,
OL,17,Fmaintenance and a proactive approach
OL,18,Fto flytipping from Bristol Waste.
OL,26,@sD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
