FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,FEmma added: "We're trying to change
OL,7,Fthe process so it's not just a system
OL,8,Fdesigned to waste time and fail,
OL,9,Fleaving waste lying on the streets
OL,10,Falmost permanently. We're trying to
OL,11,Fchallenge this. We've been trying for
OL,12,Ftwo years now.
OL,14,F"We've just been left to slide back
OL,15,Finto squalor while we've been going
OL,16,Fround and round with various meetings;
OL,17,Fwe want Bristol Waste to report
OL,18,Fflytipping themselves."
OL,26,@nD@MOUvD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
