OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,F"The state of my communal bin is hell.
OL,7,FIf you want to see a shanty town,
OL,8,Fthat's it. I can't take going down
OL,9,Fthere every two days, dealing with a
OL,10,Fwretched stinking bin."
OL,12,FBristol Waste say they are aware of
OL,13,Fthe issues and are holding sessions
OL,14,Fwith residents to improve the
OL,15,Fsituation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
