OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,FDirector Hannah Sturman said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand the people are rightly
OL,8,Ffrustrated in the area. We really want
OL,9,Fto make a difference, and I'm
OL,10,Fpersonally committed to seeing the
OL,11,Fchange that residents want.
OL,13,F"We're holding sessions to see what
OL,14,Fthe issues are that people are
OL,15,Fexperiencing on their streets, and
OL,16,Fthen that gives us the opportunity to
OL,17,Fsee - what can we do better? Are there
OL,18,Fthings that we can be doing
OL,19,Fdifferently, or are there bigger
OL,20,Finterventions needed with the council?
OL,26,@nD@_OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
