SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1772301852
OL,3,C'We're sliding back into squalor': St
OL,4,CPauls residents demand cleaner streets
OL,6,F"If we look at the data, when the on-
OL,7,Fstreet bins and mini recycling centres
OL,8,Fwere brought in, this area looked a
OL,9,Flot different; it is now more densely
OL,10,Fpopulated. There is flytipping, and
OL,11,Fpeople need to be aware they can't
OL,12,Fleave large items there."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]
